quences such as disciplinary action or termination.\n\n6. **Confidentiality**: Whistleblowers’ identities will be kept confidential as much as the law permits.\n\n7. **Investigation**: All reported incidents will be investigated promptly and thoroughly.\n\nThis policy highlights Contoso's commitment to ethical and responsible behavior, ensuring employee safety and promoting accountability throughout the organization.","annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://microsoft.sharepoint.com/teams/SharePointDemo/Shared%20Documents/employee_handbook.pdf","start_index":1409,"end_index":1421,"title":"https://microsoft.sharepoint.com/teams/SharePointDemo/Shared Documents/employee_handbook.pdf"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://microsoft.sharepoint.com/teams/SharePointDemo/Shared%20Documents/Extended_Contoso_Copilot_vs_Azure_Agents_Analysis.docx","start_index":1409,"end_index":1421,"title":"https://microsoft.sharepoint.com/teams/SharePointDemo/Shared Documents/Extended_Contoso_Copilot_vs_Azure_Agents_Analysis.docx"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://microsoft.sharepoint.com/teams/SharePointDemo/Shared%20Documents/Contoso_Copilot_vs_Azure_Agents.docx","start_index":1409,"end_index":1421,"title":"https://microsoft.sharepoint.com/teams/SharePointDemo/Shared Documents/Contoso_Copilot_vs_Azure_Agents.docx"}],"logprobs":[]}]}],"parallel_tool_calls":true,"previous_response_id":null,"prompt_cache_key":null,"prompt_cache_retention":null,"reasoning":{"effort":null,"summary":null},"safety_identifier":null,"service_tier":"default","store":true,"temperature":1.0,"text":{"format":{"type":"text"},"verbosity":"medium"},"tool_choice":"required","tools":[{"type":"sharepoint_grounding_preview","sharepoint_grounding_preview":{"project_connections":[{"project_connection_id":"/subscriptions/921496dc-987f-410f-bd57-426eb2611356/resourceGroups/agents-e2e-tests-westus2/providers/Microsoft.CognitiveServices/accounts/e2e-tests-westus2-account/projects/e2e-tests-westus2/connections/shar